Here are your most recent purchases<br>

<%@positive.each do |trans|%>
  <%= link_to "#{trans.name}", "/transactions/#{:id}" %>
  <%=number_to_currency(trans.amount)%>
  <%=trans.date.to_date%><br>
  <%=trans.id%>
  <%=trans.category_id%>
  <%@p_total += trans.amount%>
<%end%>
Here is the total of your purchases
<%=p_total%>

Here are the most recent credits to your account<br>
<%@negative.each do |trans|%>
  <%=link_to "#{trans.name}", "/transactions/#{:id}" %>
  <%=number_to_currency(trans.amount)%>
  <%=trans.date.to_date%><br>
  <%n_total += trans.total%>
<%end%>
Here is the total of the credits
<%=number_to_currency(n_total)